title: Simon Sues
description: In the Fiend world, once a contract is made your soul is as good as devoured. Humans have no hope for survival and no form of defense. That is unless they find themselves a good lawyer. Simon, once brilliant law student now turned legal council against the occult, vows to beat these demons at their own games and defeat a prince of Fiends who's after his own soul. It's the age old Faustian tale, but this time Faust has a killer lawyer!
